title: Nokia Security Code Calculator [aram89]
description:
Nokia Master Security Code Calculator
-------------------------------------

A master code is used to override the Nokia security code. If you have forgotten your security code, you can use a generated code instead. The mastercode can be used to change the old Security code.

Description
===========
The default security code for NOKIA is 12345
Suppose you set the security code on your nokia phone or your friend changed it on his phone.
And you forgot it, you can use this program to produce a universal code for your phone and reset the code to 12345.
The security code is a key feature of nokia.
It can be used to even lock the keypad of the phone.

Instruction
==========
1. Just run the program, no need for any install.
2. Press *#06# on your Nokia to get the 16 digit IMEI (International Mobile Equipment Identity) no.
3. Enter it and click generate code.
